   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00055-000-00010"/>Herrn Schrift<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>teller</addrLine><addrLine>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> med Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb412" type="place">Grillparzerstr. 7</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb51" type="place">Wien I.</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00055-000-00009"/>Lieber Doctor Schnitzler!</salute></opener><p><rs ref="#pmb10928" type="person">Otto Julius Bierbaum</rs> fordert Sie durch mich
               auf, ihm was für<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>einen <rs ref="#pmb32252" type="work">Mod. Mu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en-Almanach 1894</rs>
               zukommen zu la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en. Der Almanach er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheint <date>1. Septemb. 93</date>. Endtermin für
               die <rs type="work" ref="#pmb31965" subtype="implied">Ein<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>endung</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="underline" n="1"><date>1. Juli</date></hi>. Adre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e: <rs ref="#pmb10928" type="person">O. J. Bierbaum</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb1201" type="place"><hi rend="underline" n="1">Oberbayern</hi></rs>: <hi rend="underline" n="1">Post <rs ref="#pmb1203" type="place">Beuerberg</rs></hi>; <rs ref="#pmb1204" type="place"><hi rend="underline" n="1">Auf der Öd</hi></rs>.</p><p>Über Ihren <rs ref="#pmb29935" type="work">Anatol</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreibe ich einige <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00164-1"/>Zeilen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00164-1">nicht
                  erschienen</note> für<del rend="strikethrough">’s</del><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb29563" type="org">N. l. Bl.</rs> (<rs ref="#pmb891" type="place">Bremen</rs>) <date>1. März</date>, welche N<hi rend="superscript">r.</hi> in
               4–5000 Ex. er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinen wird. Demnäch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t erhalten Sie von mir Druck<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>orte: Aufforderung
               zur Satirenanthologie.</p><closer>Gruß u. Hand<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlag. Ihr <signed>Karl Kraus.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
